en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Skeletonized AR-15
en.description: Skeletonised AR-15 manufactured by RexTac TM. Weight reducing machining cuts into the billet lower reduce mass for decreased weight and felt inertia of recoil.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Buffer Tube
en.description: Finely tuned buffer extension for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Handguard
en.description: Carbon fiber handguard for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform. Open and lightweight construction offers optimal ergonomics for the user and gives nominal cooling factor to the barrel.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Upper Receiver
en.description: Skeletonised Upper receiver for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform. The precision machining cuts on the billet upper are great for getting gunk out of the action and reducing weight.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Muzzle Brake
en.description: A specially tuned muzzle brake for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform. Large side flutes expel gas backward, pulling the business end of the firearm forward. This, even marginally, reduces felt recoil.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Handstop
en.description: An extra handstop for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform. Inclusion requested by a man dressed as a duck wearing a hat and sunglasses.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Pistol Grip
en.description: A severely skeletonised grip for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform. Very rugged construction and ergonimics in exchange for the storage that other pistol grips might offer.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Stock
en.description: A carbon fiber wireframe stock for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform. Lightweight and sturdy, this stock provides maximum comfort for the shooter, and leaves no good place for a proper 'cheekweld'.

en.name: RexTac Wages of Sin Charging Handle
en.description: An overly skeletonised charging handle for the RexTac Wages of Sin AR platform. All unnecessary metal has been removed from this charging handle to even further reduce the weight of the platform.
